1. Install a Virtual Environment using Venv:
 - pip3 install virtualenv
 - python3 -m venv venv_sssa
 - source venv_sssa/bin/activate
   - pip3 install django

 2. Create the Project:
 - django-admin startproject sssa_project
 - python3 manage.py migrate
 - python3 manage.py runserver
 - python3 manage.py startapp sssa_app
 - python3 manage.py createsuperuser
